window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Surprise! I died...again.</b><br> <i>Except this time, I'm dead-dead.</i><br> I'm told this is the type of death that not even a phoenix can come back from....<br> <b><i>It's a good thing I suck at following the rules.</i></b></p> <p><i>Klutz: Phoenix Unleashed</i> is a steamy, action-packed, fast-paced listen. Follow our girl Ryls into death, where she continues to create chaos. Things get even more messy when she uses her power, and the power of the Queen of the Phoenix afterlife, to get back to Earth. No matter what goes wrong, there is nothing in heaven or hell that will stop Ryls from getting back to her mates.</p> <p><b>This is the final book in the But Did You Die? series and includes a HEA ending—</b><b><i>I pinky promise!</i></b></p>"; 
